OL,3,CAnas Sarwar to quit as Scottish Labour
OL,4,Cfor role in Burnham government
OL,6,FAnas Sarwar is set to quit as Scottish
OL,7,FLabour leader to be a minister in Andy
OL,8,FBurnham's Government.
OL,10,FIt is understood Sarwar will be
OL,11,Felevated to the Lords to take up a
OL,12,Fministerial post at the revamped
OL,13,FDepartment for Business, Innovation,
OL,14,FScience and Trade, headed by Jonathan
OL,15,FReynolds.
OL,17,FThe Scottish Labour leader, who called
OL,18,Ffor Sir Keir Starmer to step down as
OL,19,Fprime minister in February, is in
OL,20,FLondon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
