OL,3,CAnas Sarwar to quit as Scottish Labour
OL,4,Cfor role in Burnham government
OL,6,FHe hailed successor Burnham for his
OL,7,F"bold Labour vision" as he entered No
OL,8,F10 this week.
OL,10,FFormer Greater Manchester mayor
OL,11,FBurnham appointed his Cabinet on
OL,12,FMonday after taking office, but a raft
OL,13,Fof ministerial appointments are still
OL,14,Fto come.
OL,16,FSarwar has been Scottish Labour leader
OL,17,Fsince 2021.
OL,19,FHe said he planned to stay in his post
OL,20,Fafter Starmer's resignation in June.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@TO]
