OL,3,CAnas Sarwar to quit as Scottish Labour
OL,4,Cfor role in Burnham government
OL,6,FAsked if he planned to serve for the
OL,7,Ffive-year Holyrood term as party
OL,8,Fleader, Sarwar said: "That is my
OL,9,Fintention.
OL,11,F"I'm hungry for the fight ahead and I
OL,12,Fwant to play my full part in making
OL,13,Fsure this country never ends up in the
OL,14,Fhands of Nigel Farage and Reform."
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
