PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784715503
OL,3,CAnas Sarwar to quit as Scottish Labour
OL,4,Cfor role in Burnham government
OL,6,FThe SNP said it would be a "terrible
OL,7,Flook" to appoint Sarwar.
OL,9,FThe party's deputy leader Keith Brown
OL,10,FMSP said: "This is a terrible look for
OL,11,FAndy Burnham who waxed lyrical about a
OL,12,Fnew politics and devolving power `
OL,13,Fhe's just pulled the most undemocratic
OL,14,Ftrick in the Westminster book.
OL,16,F"Anas Sarwar led Scottish Labour to
OL,17,Ftheir worst ever election defeat, but
OL,18,Fas is always the case with the Labour
OL,19,FParty, there's always a cushty number
OL,20,Fin the House of Lords."
